articles.title: About this site
articles.description: This website consists of a collection of works done for courses I took during my MITB (Analytics) journey. I hope you enjoy reading them!

articles.title: Visual Analytics
articles.description:
Welcome to Che Xuan's website.

We have started the course on **ISSS608 Visual Analytics and Applications** since 16^th^ April 2022. More content will be updated under the navigation bars *DataViz Makeover* and *Take-home Exercise* as we progress further into the course.

At the moment, Take-home Exercise 1 & 2 are live and ready for viewing.
